Late show; Other artist(s): NRPS

reviews.review_text:
love it the people laughing/crying/coughing during st stephen.... didnt know i needed that, thank you? 

one of my favorite me and my uncles (right now at least). i like jerry's backing vocals and his pedal steel playing

also i like how you can hear the crowd in Uncle Johns Band.... gives it a jovial kind of feel (not that the song isnt jovial enough)

that dark star was getting no where fast once the recording clipped out. shame 

anyways... 

how can I review this? it's already dead
